Monday I went to see Blade II, and yestersay I just chilled w/ my ma, and played outside with the gazillion kids that I have grown to almost like.  And today I get a job. Through our very long conversation full of laughs and long silences I finally realized that me and him are ment to be the best buds that we are.  I don't want to like him like that anymore and I think that I am actually getting over him.  It hurts a little but it feels better too.  Time to go.  There is a Lifetimne movie on.  Peace Up

Ring Dance was fun.  I kinda wish I would of went by myself.  I am depressed.  I can't even write this journal without tearing up.  Bruce was really upset at the end of the night because he said that he wanted me to have the best time ever and he feels the night wasn't good enough.  I tried to tell him that even though after ring dance we just rode around in his car I had a great time because I was with him.  Of course I wimped out.  Is this love that I feel for him.  I get so excited and happy when I am around him that I am speechless.  I am never speechless!!!  I wish I could just tell him how I feel.  That everytime I hear the phone ring I wish it was him.  Everytime he calls I would rather listen then talk because his voice comforts me.  I really think that I love him.  Whenever other guys try to talk to me I back off because I can't see myself being with someone else.  He was really sad after ring dance.  I thought I saw tears in his eyes.  I should make the first move.  The next time I see him which is soon I am going to tell him everything.

I got my nails and my feet done today.  I am almost ready.  It is so hard to type with these things.  I am still waiting for bruce to call me. 

   Dinner tonight: Curly Fries

Today my mom made me call Bruce at work so that they could talk.  When she got off the phone she was smiling really hard.  I was like Ma, why are you cheesin?  She said that Bruce is the perfect gentleman and she is very impressed.  They talked about my corsage and she offered to pay for dinner and my pictures.  She said that Bruce said" Mam I am offended that you asked.  I am the perfect gentleman and I intend on treating your daughter like the perfect young lady she is."  I was cheesin hard.  I am happy. He's paying for everything down to the pictures even though I don't want him to my mom said he insisted.  My dress is all fine.  It looks a lot better and now I am excited all over again.  Me and Bruce are leaving Ring Dance early, but we don't know what to do. I NEED SUGGESTIONS!!!!!!

My dress looks horrible!!!! It is soooooooo big. I feel like a big red dumbo.  My mom said, "Oh Ashlee, it isn't bad" my dad said" I think it should be tighter."  This is what I get for being a procrastinator!!! Why does one of my genes have to say LOSER! I'm not going to be upset though, I'm going to breathe and think about good things.  The only thing good I can think of is "the sub" running into a tree, or cutting off his overgrown gigantic nose that I can see from the end of the hallway.  Now that is a lot better.  Good thoughts bring good feelings. 
  I HATE CHEMISTRY!!!!!!!!! ( PIZZA DUNKS)

So I finally have a live journal.  I have only been waiting forever to get one.  Now I can talk about the "sub" and he he likes to stare at butts and I can talk about "Hopper" and everyone else in the world cuz that is what I do.  Not really.  This is so cool.  I know this entry sucks but give me time, I'll get the hang of it, I hope.
